		'The generated secret key from the [CloudFlare Turnstile dashboard](https://dash.cloudflare.com/?to=/:account/turnstile).' => 'A [CloudFlare Turnstile vezérlőpultján](https://dash.cloudflare.com/?to=/:account/turnstile) létrehozott titkos kulcs.',
